Class PreferenceObject

java.lang.Object
gw.api.web.prefs.PreferenceObject
public class PreferenceObject extends Object
A simple wrapper of Map that only allows certain types of values.

      Parameters:
      key - the key to store the preference under
      value - the value of the preference
